## Summary
Nami is a platform for in-app purchases and subscriptions that integrates with Amplitude to send monetization data, offering no-code paywalls, targeted campaigns, and real-time revenue analytics. The integration requires a paid Nami plan and matching user identifiers between both platforms.

## Keywords
- subscription management
- no-code paywalls
- in-app purchases
- revenue analytics
- monetization optimization
- customer conversion campaigns
- user segmentation
- API key integration
- raw events
- cross-platform (mobile, tablet, TV)